title: Buying mood lifts sales and price of pre-owned homes (Shanghai Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Shanghai Municipal Government ) The sales and price of pre-owned homes rose in Shanghai in September as buying sentiment among owners continued for another month. About 36, 000 units of pre-owned properties, mainly houses, were sold
